<chapter id="chrefdetpane">
  <title>The Details Pane</title>

  <sect1>
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para><xref linkend="figrefdetailsoverview"/> shows the Details
      Pane.</para>

    <!-- This should be a comprehensive picture. In fact its just the minimum
         at the moment. It would be good to put some bubbles on this one
         pointing things out as well. -->

    <figure id="figrefdetailsoverview" float="1">
      <title>Overview of the Details Pane</title>

      <screenshot><mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata format="GIF" align="center"
                     fileref="images/reference/detailsoverview.gif"/>
        </imageobject>

        <textobject>
          <para>The ArgoUML Details Pane. A rectangular pane, with a series
            of eight tabs along the top, labelled from left to right
            <literal>To&nbsp;Do&nbsp;Item</literal>,
            <literal>Properties</literal>, <literal>Documentation</literal>,
            <literal>Style</literal>, <literal>Source</literal>,
            <literal>Constraints</literal>, <literal>Tagged Values</literal>
            and <literal>Checklist</literal>. The body of a pane is a menu of
            items to be checked, selected or entered specific to the
            particular tab selected.</para>
        </textobject>
      </mediaobject></screenshot>
    </figure>

    <para>For any entity within the system, this Pane is where all its
      associated data is entered.</para>

    <para>The Pane has a series of tabs at the top. The body of a pane is a
      menu of items to be checked, selected or entered specific to the
      particular tab selected.</para>

    <para>Of these, the <literal>Properties</literal> Tab is by far the most
      complex, with a different presentation for each entity within the
      system. Its description forms the bulk of this section.</para>
  </sect1>

